Functional Requirements
-	log in
-	Search for books by title or author and see available ones
-	View borrowing information
-	Borrow & return books
-	Hold borrowed books (Once a book is returned, it goes to the next member that has preserved that book). If 3 days have passed, the system will count as an expire preservation and put the book back to the shelf/catalogue.
-	Update, add or remove books
-	 Show overdue books
-	Generate reports
-	Notifications for members
-	Setting up maximum book a member can borrow (5)

Non-functional Requirements
-	The procedure of borrowing, reserving and returning books should be quick.
-	The interface of the application should be easy to navigate.
-	All members must be able to log in with their chosen password.
-	The system should be usable most times and not crash when handling many inputs by members.
